Sometimes called "Khoravaran," this creole [[language]] of [[Common]] and [[Aerenese]] developed in the city of [[Thaliost]], which boasted a large [[half-elf]] community before the [[Last War]]. Today, the language can be heard at half-elf unity dinners at any city of the [[Five Nations]].